Your task is to identify cell lines used in a differential expression experiment and find suitable ontology terms. These experiments may be RNA sequencing or microarray experiments. You will be given a json input containing information about experiment design, sample metadata and if available, methods sections of the associated papers.

In addition, the input will also include cell lines and their descriptions that is believed to be used in this experiment as inferred by you in a previous run, and a list of ontology terms that were deemed to be possible matches to these results based on cosine similarity to your previous inference.

Look for suitable ontology terms within the list of ontology terms based on the information about the paper provided to you and return them in the json format provided. Do not return anything apart from the json output.
